---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ - LbisTech" description="Frequently asked questions about LbisTech courses and enrollment">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-900 to-primary-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Find answers to common questions about our courses, enrollment, and learning process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- General Questions -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">General Questions</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>What is LbisTech?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>LbisTech is a professional technology education platform that offers comprehensive certification programs in cloud computing, DevOps, and emerging technologies. We focus on hands-on learning and industry-relevant skills to prepare students for successful tech careers.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>Who can enroll in LbisTech courses?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Our courses are designed for IT professionals, students, and career changers at all levels. Whether you're a beginner looking to enter the tech industry or an experienced professional wanting to upgrade your skills, we have programs suitable for your needs.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>What makes LbisTech different from other training providers?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>We combine theoretical knowledge with practical, hands-on experience using real-world scenarios. Our instructors are industry professionals with extensive experience, and we provide personalized support throughout your learning journey. We also offer flexible learning options and lifetime access to course materials.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Course Questions -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Course Information</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>How long do the courses take to complete?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Course durations vary depending on the program. Most courses range from 6-16 weeks, with AWS and Azure certifications typically taking 10-12 weeks, DevOps Engineering taking 16 weeks, and Docker Containerization taking 8 weeks. You can learn at your own pace with our flexible scheduling.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>Are there any prerequisites for the courses?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Prerequisites vary by course. Beginner courses like Open Source VoIP have minimal requirements, while intermediate and advanced courses may require basic IT knowledge or prior experience. Each course page lists specific prerequisites, and our team can help assess your readiness during enrollment.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>Do I get a certificate after completion?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Yes! Upon successful completion of each course, you'll receive a LbisTech certificate of completion. Our certification programs also prepare you for industry-recognized certifications from AWS, Microsoft Azure, and other leading technology providers.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>Can I access course materials after completion?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Absolutely! Once you enroll in a course, you get lifetime access to all course materials, including videos, labs, and resources. You can revisit content anytime and access updates as we enhance the curriculum.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Enrollment & Payment -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Enrollment & Payment</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>How do I enroll in a course?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Enrollment is simple! Browse our courses, select the one you're interested in, and click "Enroll Now." Fill out the enrollment form with your details and learning goals. Our team will contact you within 24 hours to complete the process and provide next steps.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>What payment methods do you accept?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>We accept various payment methods including credit cards, debit cards, bank transfers, and online payment platforms. We also offer flexible payment plans for most courses. Contact our team for specific payment options and installment plans.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>Do you offer any free courses?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>Yes! We offer our Open Source VoIP course completely free as an introduction to our training methodology. We also provide free workshops and webinars periodically. Follow our social media channels for updates on free learning opportunities.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>What is your refund policy?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee for all paid courses. If you're not satisfied with your learning experience within the first 30 days, you can request a full refund. Contact our support team for assistance with refund requests.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Support -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <div class="p-6">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Support & Learning</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>What kind of support do you provide?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>We provide comprehensive support including live chat, email support, phone consultations, and direct access to instructors. Our support team is available Monday-Friday 9 AM-6 PM PKT, with email support available 24/7. We also have community forums for peer-to-peer learning.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>Can I get help with job placement after completing a course?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>While we don't guarantee job placement, we provide career guidance, resume review, interview preparation, and networking opportunities. Many of our graduates have successfully transitioned to new roles or advanced in their current positions after completing our programs.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question w-full flex justify-between items-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                    <span>How can I contact LbisTech for more information?</span>
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-600">
                    <p>You can reach us through multiple channels: email us at team@lbistech.com, call us at +92 03 111 088 881, or use our contact form on the website. We're based in Lahore, Pakistan, but we serve students globally. Our team typically responds within 24 hours.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Still have questions? -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Still have questions?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Can't find the answer you're looking for? Our team is here to help.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-coral-500 hover:bg-coral-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script>
  // FAQ Toggle Functionality
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
    
    faqItems.forEach(item => {
      const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');
      const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
      const icon = question.querySelector('svg');
      
      question.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const isOpen = !answer.classList.contains('hidden');
        
        if (isOpen) {
          answer.classList.add('hidden');
          icon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        } else {
          answer.classList.remove('hidden');
          icon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>